data.description: INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY TO LIVE IN THE HEART OF BUCKHEAD!  South/Sunny side of the building with skyline views!  Great price for a loft style 1 bedroom condo located behind the St. Regis Hotel.  Open and floor to ceiling windows.  High ceilings, fresh paint and secured storage unit.  Storm windows were added to enclose porch/sunroom to increase sq ft. Quiet community located at the top of cul-de-sac with POOL & ON SITE GYM. Library with free wi-fi in common area basement. HOA covers all utilities (minus phone/cable/TV).  New Paint, gleaming hardwood floors throughout sorry no pets allowed in building and no investors.  Quiet professional building. Hidden gem in the heart of Buckhead on quiet cul-de-sac behind the St. Regis
